urants.**\n    *   **Enjoy Dinner.**\n\n**Important Considerations:**\n\n*   **Travel Time:** Jharkhand has variable road conditions. Factor in extra travel time.\n*   **Respect Local Customs:** Dress modestly when visiting religious sites.\n*   **Bargaining:** Bargaining is common in local markets.\n*   **Sustainability:** Carry a reusable water bottle and avoid single-use plastics.\n\n**Once you provide me with the details requested above, I can give you a much more tailored and useful itinerary!**\n','2025-09-15 18:22:11'),('c1e538ff-35ac-40a3-95a0-d80aa70a5e7a','d3bae778-2eb0-4f8a-ab32-9cbc1976aa1a','session_1757766995292','what is the error you are getting','I\'m sorry, I\'m having trouble connecting to my AI service right now. Please try again in a moment, or contact our support team for assistance with your Jharkhand travel questions.','2025-09-13 07:07:04'),('cf76a6e0-2c18-4fdf-abd4-319468661fe1','9ffdf221-c444-4eb2-b15b-8f9693adc0b0','session_1758096448550','good','Alright! How can I help you plan your trip to Jharkhand? Do you have any specific interests, like:\n\n*   **Nature and Wildlife?** (e.g., Betla National Park, waterfalls)\n*   **Religious Sites?** (e.g., Baidyanath Temple, Parasnath Hill)\n*   **Culture and History?** (e.g., tribal villages, museums)\n*   **Adventure Activities?** (e.g., trekking, rock climbing)\n\nTell me what you\'re looking for and I\'ll give you some recommendations!\n','2025-09-17 02:41:11'),('d999e283-6b58-465f-af8f-76a521013597','d3bae778-2eb0-4f8a-ab32-9cbc1976aa1a','session_1757767426040','hi','I\'m sorry, I\'m having trouble connecting to my AI service right now. Please try again in a moment, or contact our support team for assistance with your Jharkhand travel questions.','2025-09-13 07:16:12'),('e355bc93-55cc-4bfe-b05f-353095f9a7fb','d3bae778-2eb0-4f8a-ab32-9cbc1976aa1a','session_1757767426040','hi','I\'m sorry, I\'m having trouble connecting to my AI service right now. Please try again in a moment, or contact our sup